{"tid":659724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"言語不通爆衝突 　西裝印度漢KO兩本地男","createTime":"2018-05-10T05:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T16:34:00.000Z","uid":141060,"like":230,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"69a9e4a2e00de0d38afdd53e60e28d19ed74aed2","tid":659724,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180510/mobile/bkn-20180510043700365-0510_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180510%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180510043700365-0510_00822_001.html&d=6g8Pjpt9%2FBMQVyvpCJs%2FEZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=34dbf6f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180510/mobile/bkn-20180510043700365-0510_00822_001.html</a><br />\n印度漢與2本地男互毆俱傷。現場土瓜灣美景街45號一間燒烤店，昨(9日)晚11時許，2名同為43歲姓黃及姓陳本地男子，在上址消夜，期間疑有人嬉皮笑臉出言「撩女仔」，企圖搭訕鄰枱一名印度籍女子，惹起女方同行穿西裝41歲同鄉男友人Singh極為不滿，挺身護花出言向對方指摘。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雙方因此發生口角，並愈吵愈烈，繼而動手，2本地男與印度漢由店內追打至店外，3人於街頭扭打，其中一名本地男不敵，被印度漢打至頸及面受傷，倒臥於路上，另一本地男面及口受傷，食客見狀致電報警。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕至，迅速控制場面，並向各人了解情況，涉案3男俱傷，印度漢面，手及胸受傷，拒絕送院，2本地男則由救護車送院救治，其中被打至瞓地受傷的黃，送院後情況嚴重。3人涉嫌在公眾地方打架被拘捕，案件交九龍城警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/132749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F132749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=430cfb19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f45c497016c1e00ed5ab0bf25fa443800000ed65","tid":659724,"uid":49392,"like":7,"dislike":123,"score":-116,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:30:48.000Z","msg":"連登仔：多謝張超雄"},{"pid":"8198fe1e81a8e3b41951c70d25d389d53718f27a","tid":659724,"uid":35430,"like":157,"dislike":2,"score":155,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n叫左唔好學咩詠春架啦，又唔識護頭護頸"},{"pid":"b8b0c1a98f5bb8c56f429cc1f41e66ecfb7da247","tid":659724,"uid":53026,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:32:50.000Z","msg":"印度張晉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02af7334e3fe5af7ac6f2ce998decec6006bd88","tid":659724,"uid":5303,"like":670,"dislike":8,"score":662,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:33:11.000Z","msg":"印度仔撩港女，咁港男打柒印度仔都好正常，咁港果撩印度女，咁人地印度仔打柒你都好正常"},{"pid":"7b6f186af598ec5c96049860b4bb49dc02bb218a","tid":659724,"uid":35430,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:33:48.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n叫左唔好學咩詠春架啦，又唔識護頭護頸"},{"pid":"db33927bbcce9b86806ec2092de2d9a9d9e53560","tid":659724,"uid":99205,"like":111,"dislike":9,"score":102,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:36:07.000Z","msg":"港豬抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n有時不得不贊同五毛分化<br />\n<br />\n上一代D阿叔沒咩讀過書,又唔肯操體能<br />\n平時鬧D後生就大大聲<br />\n要真打上來就廢到2打1都輸<br />\n大佬人地中東人閒閒地托得起自己倍幾體重既野<br />\n你呢D港豬阿叔去公園玩下正手引體上升,一下都未必得啦<br />\n聊人打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e9a97a9d48323fb3fa8744c07441e1ebe71311","tid":659724,"uid":67500,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"如果本地男俾印度人撩女仔，反而縮頭龜"},{"pid":"b94b7295fd7337b6e2ba25695fcad2679d147820","tid":659724,"uid":2419,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:51:18.000Z","msg":"柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8085ad3d057ccf07324fb62cabf70be45faa08d2","tid":659724,"uid":28831,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T05:51:30.000Z","msg":"有仔都夠膽撩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c467b7c2a455df482ccd732e84270395d8f24b5c","tid":659724,"uid":141060,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"印度漢面，手及胸受傷，拒絕送院，2本地男則由救護車送院救治，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其中被打至瞓地受傷的黃，送院後情況嚴重</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adef617590bffec296c957506e9f2fee4